    's09.p3':'They are accustomed to working in demanding industrial environments such as automotive, manufacturing, energy, and construction sectors. We offer competitive and transparent pricing, the flexibility to scale the workforce up or down based on project needs, and if required, our workers come equipped with their own PPE and tools. With fast mobilization and reliable performance, our multilingual supervisors (EN/DE) ensure effective communication throughout your project. We can also provide assistant welders, fitters, locksmiths, and complete installation teams as needed.',
    's09.welding_caps_h':'Welding Capabilities',
